description.en: Cozy dormitory with all amenities: Wi-Fi, washing machine, bathroom, and kitchen available. A great option for comfortable living!

description.en: The apartment includes: Phone, Cable TV, Internet, Air Conditioning, Balcony, TV, Kitchen, Refrigerator, Washing machine
